Dave Chappelle's Block Party;;74;;92;;R;;Actor, writer and comic Dave Chappelle loads up a bus with residents of his Ohio hometown and takes them to Brooklyn, N.Y. Once there, the travelers enjoy a concert featuring Kanye West, the Fugees, Big Daddy Kane and others. Rehearsal footage and Chappelle's brand of comedy enliven the proceedings.;;Music,Documentary,Comedy;;Michel Gondry;;2005;;Dave Chappelle;;https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/block_party